      • nextTokenAsync

        CompletableFuture<Long> nextTokenAsync(Set<UUID> streams,
                                       long numTokens)
        Asynchronously retrieve the next token in the sequence, given a set of streams.
        Parameters:
        streams - The set of streams to retrieve the next token for.
        numTokens - The number of tokens to acquire, 0 means to just fetch the head of the stream.
        Returns:
        The next token in the sequence, which is contiguous for numToken tokens.
